latestIgtvVideos.title: YOGA SE HI HOGA🙌
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
108 Suryanamaskaar w @ahuti_velani

Last week on Friday we decided to give it a try. As we wanted to check our strength and ability. 
So, on Friday onwards we started our practice with 15 suryanamaskaar.Then we gradually kept adding 15 Suryanamaskaar every day.
We were not jaded throughout & the experience was ecstatic. 
After accomplishing 108 suryanamaskaar we have realised that it is all in our mind. Convincing our mind is all we have to do to attain the goal that we have set. 
Your mental ability is everything that decides whether to ceaselessly keep going or to stop. 
And rest the experience was worth everything :)🌼
